# Profile calibration

- If `LEARNING-PROFILE` is present: match depth; don't re-teach covered; don't skip fundamentals at beginner.
- If missing: `python3 ~/.cursor/learning/cli.py show` before inventing level/history.
- If empty: don't invent history; send user to `/study-log` (not `/study-plan`).
